hard</persName><date when="1893-09-13">14. 9. 1893</date><placeName ref="#pmb33978">Znaim</placeName></correspAction><correspContext><ref type="belongsToCorrespondence" target="#pmb10863">Beer-Hofmann, Richard</ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCollection" target="L00261">Hofmannsthal an Schnitzler, [9. 9. 1893]</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCollection" target="L00263">Bahr an Schnitzler, 17. 9. 1893</ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L00260">Schnitzler, Salten an Beer-Hofmann, 27. 8. 1893</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L00264">Schnitzler, Goldmann an Beer-Hofmann, 18. 9. 1893</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
